Seems to be identical issue with ICU not playing nice with the build environment.
There is an ICU fix already for Chromium / Iridium / Ungoogled-Chromium builds that suffered build failures due to pretty much the exact same reason.
THAT fix can be found here & I can confirm it works for the browsers:
https://reviews.freebsd.org/D39564

We need a similar patch that "translates" "U_FINAL=final" / "U_NOEXCEPT=noexcept" / "U_OVERRIDE=override"  etc and whatever else ICU fettles with.
